er tube coincidence counter for lower atmosphere radiosonde measurements.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>The Review of scientific instruments</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/b99c2c46b5f9d8734718d32cc35ac7ef"><gtr:id>b99c2c46b5f9d8734718d32cc35ac7ef</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Harrison RG</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2013-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0034-6748</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/A435D30D-954F-49FD-9E9B-4AEC72238751"><gtr:id>A435D30D-954F-49FD-9E9B-4AEC72238751</gtr:id><gtr:title>Vertical profile measurements of lower troposphere ionisation</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Journal of Atmospheric and Solar-Terrestrial Physics</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/0d2b9ffc72371ff3aac01acd79f7be7f"><gtr:id>0d2b9ffc72371ff3aac01acd79f7be7f</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Harrison R</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2014-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/13264D0E-1C7D-4131-B75A-243B462051B8"><gtr:id>13264D0E-1C7D-4131-B75A-243B462051B8</gtr:id><gtr:title>Detection of lower tropospheric responses to solar energetic particles at midlatitudes.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Physical review letters</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/1c1f1636941b6bc37c0ad42d92698b20"><gtr:id>1c1f1636941b6bc37c0ad42d92698b20</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Nicoll KA</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2014-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0031-9007</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/6993B68F-46BF-4836-8B5A-96F28F815AFF"><gtr:id>6993B68F-46BF-4836-8B5A-96F28F815AFF</gtr:id><gtr:title>Stratiform cloud electrification: comparison of theory with multiple in-cloud measurements</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTi